---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About Ichthyosis · For Olivia">
  <Header />

  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight">
      About Ichthyosis
    </h1>

    <p class="mt-6 text-gray-700">
      Ichthyosis is a group of genetic skin conditions. It often causes skin to
      become very dry, thick, and prone to cracking. Severity varies from person
      to person.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-semibold">Day-to-day impact</h2>
    <ul class="mt-4 list-disc pl-5 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
      <li>Regular moisturising and skin care routines</li>
      <li>Managing discomfort, overheating, or sensitivity</li>
      <li>Extra time and cost for daily care and products</li>
      <li>Ongoing medical support depending on severity</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="mt-10 rounded-2xl border border-black/10 bg-white p-6">
      <h3 class="font-semibold">Trusted resources</h3>
      <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700 text-sm">
        We’ll add links to trusted organisations here (e.g. Ichthyosis Support Group, NHS) once finalised.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
